- Section::inject('page_title', $project->title)
- Section::inject('page_action', "Select a Template")
- Section::inject('active_subnav', 'create')
- Section::inject('no_page_header', true)

!{View::make('projects.partials.toolbar')->with('project', $project)}


- if ($templates):

  h5 Select a Template

  p
    | Here are some statements of work from real, successful procurements for the same type of project you're doing.
    | When you "fork" one of these templates, we'll grab all the good bits and then let you customize it to suit the
    | details of your specific project.

  ul.templates-list
    !{View::make('projects.partials.template_lis')->with('templates', $templates)->with('project', $project)}
    - if ($more_templates_count):
      li.show-more
        a.show-more-templates-link(data-href="#{route('project_more_templates', array($project->id))}") See #{$more_templates_count} more #{Str::plural('template', $more_templates_count)}...
        img.spinner(src="#{asset('img/spinner.gif')}")


  h5 ...Or Start From Scratch

  p
    | Prefer to roll your own SOW? That's great too! You'll still have access to our library of pre-written sections.

  .centered
    a.btn.btn-primary(href="#{route('project_background', array($project->id))}") Start From Scratch

- else:

  p.well
    | <strong>Welcome to SOW Composer!</strong> In the future, we hope to have a library of SOW templates that
    | can help you get a running start. For now, you're the first in our system to use the <em>#{$project->project_type->name}</em>
    | project type, so we'll walk you through the SOW creation process from the start.

    .centered
      a.btn.btn-primary(href="#{route('project_background', array($project->id))}") Let's get started! &rarr;
